sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Browser as Trình duyệt (Client)
    participant Container as JSP Container (Tomcat)
    participant MainJSP as Main.jsp (Source)
    participant Fragment as Fragment.jsp (Include file)
    participant Servlet as Generated Servlet (Java)

    Note over Container, Servlet: Giai đoạn Dịch (Translation Phase)
    Container->>MainJSP: Đọc nội dung file chính
    Container->>Fragment: Đọc nội dung file được include
    Note right of Container: Gộp nội dung Fragment vào Main
    Container->>Servlet: Biên dịch thành 1 file .java/.class duy nhất

    Note over Browser, Servlet: Giai đoạn Yêu cầu (Request Phase)
    Browser->>Container: Gửi HTTP Request (ví dụ: main.jsp)
    Container->>Servlet: Thực thi logic Servlet
    Servlet-->>Container: Trả về luồng HTML đã gộp
    Container-->>Browser: Trả về 1 file HTML duy nhất